{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: #e0b0b0;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #333;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #a00000;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #f5dada;\n            color: #333;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a00000 0%, #e0b0b0 100%);\n            opacity: 0.2;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .collection-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .collection-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .collection-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .collection-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 300px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .collection-item-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .collection-item-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: #a00000;\n        }\n        .collection-item-info p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #7d0000;\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #e0b0b0;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#collection\">Collection</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Sustainable Style, Timeless Design</h2>\n            <p>Discover fashion that feels good, looks good, and does good. We craft beautiful, long-lasting garments with the planet in mind.</p>\n            <a href=\"#collection\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Our Latest Collection</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; color: #a00000;\">Our Commitment</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1em;\">At Evergreen Threads, we believe in a future where fashion nurtures the environment. We meticulously source organic, recycled, and innovative eco-friendly materials, ensuring fair labor practices throughout our supply chain. Our designs are created to be versatile, durable, and to transcend fleeting trends, encouraging a more conscious approach to your wardrobe.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"collection\">\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; color: #a00000; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Our Latest Collection</h2>\n            <div class=\"collection-grid\">\n                <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/e0b0b0/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Dress\">\n                    <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Organic Linen Dress</h3>\n                        <p>Effortlessly chic and breathable, made from 100% GOTS-certified organic linen.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/a00000/ffffff?text=Recycled+Tee\" alt=\"Recycled T-Shirt\">\n                    <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Recycled Cotton Tee</h3>\n                        <p>A soft, everyday essential crafted from premium recycled cotton fibers.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/f5dada/ffffff?text=Hemp+Pants\" alt=\"Hemp Pants\">\n                    <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Durable Hemp Trousers</h3>\n                        <p>Stylish and robust, made from sustainably grown hemp for longevity.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; background-color: #e0b0b0; border-radius: 8px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 2em; color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Connect With Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Have questions or want to learn more about our practices?</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: #333; color: #fff;\">Get In Touch</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Ethically made, sustainably sourced.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}